'''OMGPop'''是一个现已倒闭的游戏工作室，于2013年7月被Zynga收购，游戏形式为“在线”、“多人”，以[[Adobe_Flash|Adobe Flash]]为基本框架。<ref>{{cite web |first=Sean |last=Hollister |url=http://www.theverge.com/2013/6/3/4393694/draw-something-studio-omgpop-reportedly-shuttered-amid-zynga-layoffs |title='Draw Something' studio OMGPOP reportedly shuttered amid Zynga layoffs |work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]] |date=2013-06-03 |accessdate=2013-06-26 |archive-date=2013-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130628231631/http://www.theverge.com/2013/6/3/4393694/draw-something-studio-omgpop-reportedly-shuttered-amid-zynga-layoffs |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 历史 ==
OMGPop在[[纽约|纽约市]][[苏荷区|苏荷区]]成立。成立之初，OMGPop的资金主要来自Y Combinator，此后OMPop开始逐渐壮大起来。2009年，OMGPop的官网omgpop.com被《[[时代周刊|时代周刊]]》列为50个最佳的网站之一。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/03/21/omgpop-iminlikewithyou-ycombinator|title=OMGPOP's Sale to Zynga is One of Y Combinator's Biggest Exits to Date|accessdate=2013-01-28|date=2012-03-21|last=Cutler|first=Kim-Mai|publisher=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|archive-date=2012-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102105141/http://techcrunch.com/2012/03/21/omgpop-iminlikewithyou-ycombinator/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年3月21日，Zynga宣布收购OMGPOP为，价格为1.8亿美元。Zynga表示：“为消费者提供好玩、免费游戏是我们的使命。我们坚信，OMGPOP将帮助我们实现我们的承诺。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/03/21/done-deal-zynga-gets-draw-something-phenom-by-acquiring-omgpop-were-hearing-210m/|title=Done Deal: Zynga Gets "Draw Something" Phenom bBy Acquiring OMGPOP|accessdate=21 March 2012|date=2012-03-21|last=Cutler|first=Kim-Mai|publisher=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|archive-date=2016-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160926113205/https://techcrunch.com/2012/03/21/done-deal-zynga-gets-draw-something-phenom-by-acquiring-omgpop-were-hearing-210m/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/26/technology/draw-something-changes-the-game-quickly-for-omgpop.html|title=Draw Something Changes the Game Quickly for Omgpop|date=25 March 2012|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|last2=Wortham|first2=Jenna|first1=Brian X.|last1=Chen|accessdate=2016-08-18|archive-date=2016-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310164007/http://www.nytimes.com/2012/03/26/technology/draw-something-changes-the-game-quickly-for-omgpop.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2013年6月3日，Zynga的首席执行官马克·平卡斯在官方博客宣布，Zynga将重组公司、削减财政，18％的员工将会被解雇，许多OMGPOP的老员工因此被解雇，此后OMGPop便关闭了。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blog.zynga.com/2013/06/03/ceo-update-4|title=CEO Update|date=3 June 2013|last=Pincus|first=Mark|work=Zynga|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603231628/http://blog.zynga.com/2013/06/03/ceo-update-4/|archivedate=2013年6月3日|accessdate=2016年8月18日}}</ref>但是OMGPop的官网omgpop.com却依旧保持活跃。但2013年7月时Zynga发表了一份声明，宣布官网将于2013年9月30日关闭，Cupcake Corner、Gem Rush、Pool World Champ以及Snoops4款游戏也将于2013年8月29日停止运营。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/06/04/zynga-shuts-down-omgpop-one-year-after-acquiring-it-for-200m/|title=Zynga Shuts Down OMGPOP One Year After Acquiring It For $200M|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2013-06-04|last=Kumparak|first=Greg|publisher=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|archive-date=2013-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627081036/http://techcrunch.com/2013/06/04/zynga-shuts-down-omgpop-one-year-after-acquiring-it-for-200m/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://venturebeat.com/2013/06/03/zynga-may-be-shutting-omgpop-game-studio-that-it-bought-for-180m/|title=Zynga may be closing Omgpop game studio that it bought for $180M|accessdate=2013-06-26|date=2013-06-03|last=Takahashi|first=Dean|publisher=[[VentureBeat|VentureBeat]]|archive-date=2013-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130705065744/http://venturebeat.com/2013/06/03/zynga-may-be-shutting-omgpop-game-studio-that-it-bought-for-180m/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="closure">{{Cite web|url=http://www.zyngaplayersupport.com/article/all/Announcement-OMGPOPcom-Closure-en_US-1375113624757|title=Zynga Support|accessdate=2016-08-18|date=2016-07-29|last=jboeger|work=www.zyngaplayersupport.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151211050753/https://www.zyngaplayersupport.com/article/all/Announcement-OMGPOPcom-Closure-en_US-1375113624757|archivedate=2015-12-11}}</ref><ref name="closuregames">{{Cite web|url=http://www.zyngaplayersupport.com/article/all/Announcement-OMGPOPcom-Game-Closures-en_US-1375114847142|title=Zynga Support|accessdate=2016-08-18|date=2016-07-29|last=jboeger|work=www.zyngaplayersupport.com|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151210202554/https://www.zyngaplayersupport.com/article/all/Announcement-OMGPOPcom-Game-Closures-en_US-1375114847142|archivedate=2015-12-10}}</ref>
==开发的游戏==
OMGPop的游戏涵盖了卡牌类、体育类等，以及[[导弹指挥官|导弹指挥官]]的特别版等。Draw My Thing是OMGPop的代表作。据2012年3月16日的一则报道显示，Draw My Thing是Facebook上最受欢迎的游戏，超过1080万名日活跃用户痴迷于此，而Zynga的Words with Friends只有860万名日活跃用户。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://arcade-junkies.com/2009/11/atari-now-offering-free-classic-arcade-games-online/ |title=Atari Now Offering Free Classic Arcade Games Online |accessdate=2010-07-20 |date=2009-11-24 |publisher=Arcade-Junkies |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100505030856/http://arcade-junkies.com/2009/11/atari-now-offering-free-classic-arcade-games-online/ |archivedate=2010-05-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

